    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039500/extras/21b7094de51e5621a8d45883f18a8bcf.avif?t=1769088341\" width=1530 height=378 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039500/extras/bd3d51ad2224c2927d5f56d5db02da18.avif?t=1769088341\" width=960 height=1706 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《万象群侠传》是一款轻量型的PC单机武侠角色扮演小游戏。我们构建了一个轻松纯粹的武侠江湖。在这里，你可以邂逅红颜知己，结交各路英侠，修炼各家武学，踏上一段段充满奇遇的江湖之旅。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>交结五都 侠骨柔情</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >结交性格迥异的伙伴好友</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >邂逅百态千姿的知己红颜</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039500/extras/95515641d2ce0859bad52104df42a903.poster.avif?t=1769088341\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039500/extras/95515641d2ce0859bad52104df42a903.webm?t=1769088341\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039500/extras/95515641d2ce0859bad52104df42a903.mp4?t=1769088341\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>刀光剑影 恩怨情仇</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >相逢一笑，与各路江湖高手杯酒言欢</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当仁不让，同江湖奇人异士一较短长</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039500/extras/7b7972d1900fe79548e7fc2550161a12.poster.avif?t=1769088341\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039500/extras/7b7972d1900fe79548e7fc2550161a12.webm?t=1769088341\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039500/extras/7b7972d1900fe79548e7fc2550161a12.mp4?t=1769088341\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>江湖门派 武林绝学</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >加入不同门派，体验别样江湖人生</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集各家功法，搭配独特武学战术</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039500/extras/a8703af02a8fd82ceeca88231dd20996.poster.avif?t=1769088341\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039500/extras/a8703af02a8fd82ceeca88231dd20996.webm?t=1769088341\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>江湖风华 红尘万象</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游历山川胜境品味江湖风华，衡山雾凇，黄州三绝，汝城香龙，花药春溪......</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >结识三教九流修习红尘百艺，琴棋书画，医卜毒御，佛道儒墨，诗词百戏......</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039500/extras/3246bc50778ef2d094e73cd8345784ac.poster.avif?t=1769088341\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039500/extras/3246bc50778ef2d094e73cd8345784ac.mp4?t=1769088341\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
